        "content": "<p>I'm pondering this CodeSystem: <a href=\"https://www.hl7.org/fhir/v2/0360/2.7/v2-0360-2.7.cs.json.html\">https://www.hl7.org/fhir/v2/0360/2.7/v2-0360-2.7.cs.json.html</a></p>\n<p>Specifically this bit:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"JSON\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nt\">\"url\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v2-0360|2.7\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"nt\">\"version\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"0360\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"nt\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"v2.0360.2.7\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"nt\">\"title\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"v2 table 0360, Version 2.7\"</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>This is obviously the codesystem for HL7v2 table 0360 from the HL7v2 2.7 spec. Is this codesystem right though?</p>\n<p>Why is the version set to <code>\"0360\"</code>? Why is there a version included in the <code>\"url\"</code>?</p>\n<p>I would have expected</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"JSON\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nt\">\"url\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v2-0360\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"nt\">\"version\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"2.7\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n</code></pre></div>",
